Reasoning: The paper discusses a dataset designed for deep learning techniques in robotic vision problems, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The dataset is also generated using virtual reality technology, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The large-scale nature of the dataset and the use of data-driven techniques suggest that it could also fall under machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper mentions annotations and semantic classes, which could suggest a focus on graphics (cs.GR).
